// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
//  test_physics_informed_nn.hexa — PINN (#251) tests
//
//  Verifies:
//    1. Forward pass returns finite scalar
//    2. Finite-difference derivatives on known function (nearly-linear init)
//    3. Heat residual sign / magnitude on smooth init
//    4. Burgers residual computation sanity
//    5. Data loss decreases after SGD steps on data-only
//    6. Total loss (data+PDE) decreases after training
//    7. Deep-copy property of perturb_scalar (no aliasing)
//
//  Run: ./hexa self/test_physics_informed_nn.hexa
